<BaseLayout
  title="About — Zac Culpan"
  description="Zac Culpan is a marketer, product person, and startup founder based in New Zealand. Writing about ecosystem marketing, creator marketing, and SaaS growth."
>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="post-header">
      <span class="post-tag">About</span>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}zac-headshot-final.jpg`} alt="Zac Culpan" class="about-headshot" width="120" height="120" />
      <h1 class="post-title">About</h1>
      <p class="post-desc">Marketing, product, and growth in SaaS.</p>
    </div>
    <article class="post-content">
      <p>I'm Zac. I'm a marketer and product person based in New Zealand, currently Head of Product at <a href="https://www.oneroof.co.nz" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong>OneRoof</strong></a> (NZME) and co-founding a startup in the creator marketing measurement space.</p>
      <p>Before this, I was Head of Marketing at <a href="https://www.narrative.so" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong>Narrative</strong></a>, where I spent nearly three years building the brand and growth engine for an AI-powered photo culling tool used by professional photographers worldwide. That's where most of my thinking on ecosystem marketing, creator partnerships, and community-driven growth comes from.</p>
      <p>I've also helped build other great companies across SaaS, fintech, and digital products, including <a href="https://www.poliigon.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong>Poliigon</strong></a> (working alongside <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@blenderguru" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">BlenderGuru</a>), <a href="https://www.bettersaver.co.nz" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong>BetterSaver</strong></a> (first employee), and <a href="https://www.vendhq.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong>Vend</strong></a>.</p>
      <h2>What I write about</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Ecosystem marketing</strong> — building growth through communities, partnerships, and trust</li>
        <li><strong>Creator &amp; influencer marketing</strong> — measurement, ROI, and what actually works</li>
        <li><strong>SaaS growth</strong> — strategy and frameworks for early and mid-stage companies</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Everything here comes from real experience. If I haven't done it or seen it first-hand, I don't write about it.</p>
      <h2>Get in touch</h2>
      <p>Best place to reach me is <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/zachary-culpan/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>